node.text: Showed @usweekly how I get my beauty sleep and wanted to share it with you guys too ☺️ I get asked a lot about my exact skincare routine but haven’t shown it because there’s a lot to it 😆 I wanted to be as honest as possible though so I’m showing you guys every product I use and the actual steps I use them in. Hopefully it’s helpful and if you want me to link the products in my stories for you, lmk below! 🤍

node.text:
You see us on TV and follow us on here, but there is so much more you don’t see when the cameras are off. All new episodes of Tarek’s Flip Side on the new @discoveryplus #discoveryplus 
-
Anytime I film with my honey @therealtarekelmoussa we just have the best time. You get to see a deeper look into our love and life. We get more personal, and you might find out things you never knew ☺️ make sure you check out the longer version!!

node.text:
I know you guys have been waiting to see it!! A tour of our new beach home for the rest of the year! 
-

Earlier this year @therealtarekelmoussa & I sold his “dadchelor” pad. I represented him in the sale, we got multiple offers and it sold very quick. So we were left searching for a home quick. We found this summer beach house & fell in love with it. Making new memories together in our new home. 
-

Welcome to our home!!! Come on in and take a tour with us and @people @peopletv

node.text:
Super fun filming Makeup removing tips with my bestie @drmonavand .
We all like to get dolled up, but if you don’t take your makeup off  correctly it can cause aging and breakouts. I’m constantly filming and getting my makeup done for events & @drmonavand is always filming for her YouTube channel. Between Mona and I we have some tricks and tips for you.
.
The video cuts off a little short.... all I was saying was use a warm soft white washcloth at the end  to make sure all of you makeup is off. .
Let me know what you think of this video, add a ❤️ and comment.

node.text: One year ago today I made the best decision of my life by saying yes to spending forever with the most special man. I remember when he proposed… in that moment everything melted away and I was just staring at my forever person, fully in tears thinking how lucky I was that I got to spend the rest of my life with him. ♥️ Thank you to the man who has put a smile on my face every single day. You have shown me what true love and family are all about. I fall more and more in love with you as I watch how amazing of a dad you are with the babies, how hard you work, and how you put family and your loved ones first in your life. You’re my best friend, my person, and my rock. Happy 1 year of being engaged baby! Cheers to a lifetime of You & Me ♥️

node.text:
Screaming because we got nominated for an Emmy today!!! Ah!! 🤗🏆

So proud of our show, our cast, the producers, and everyone who makes this show so special 🤍 So grateful to be doing the things I love with people I love but the best part is getting messages from you guys saying our show inspired you to get into real estate or that it pushed you to do more or be more confident etc etc because there’s literally nothing more rewarding than that 🙏🏻🤍

So beyond honored (fingers crossed) and I can’t WAIT for you guys to see season 4… I think it’s the best yet 🤫😏

node.text:
Down the river we go 😂🤍 

Had the best family day today, can’t get over how cute it was to see Tay and Bray smile all day long 🤍 The kids have been at camp most of the summer so far and we’ve been busy too so Tarek and I planned a whole surprise day for them and it was sooo much fun and much needed 🤍 I love how Tay holds my hand the whole way through the ride but it’s the “oh no oh no” at the end of the video for me 😆

node.text: Showed @usweekly how I get my beauty sleep and wanted to share it with you guys too ☺️ I get asked a lot about my exact skincare routine but haven’t shown it because there’s a lot to it 😆 I wanted to be as honest as possible though so I’m showing you guys every product I use and the actual steps I use them in. Hopefully it’s helpful and if you want me to link the products in my stories for you, lmk below! 🤍

node.text:
Summer nights with you 💛 

Two nights ago we were here on the pier, listening to good music and watching the sunset and tonight we’re in Vegas watching the @ufc fight but no matter where we are the best times are always with you ☺️ Happy weekend everyone !! Anyone watching the fight tonight or is that not your thing?

node.text:
“Mine” 😆💛

Had so much fun yesterday and it’s soo nice to be back at concerts ☺️ I took these kinds of things for granted before quarantine but now I’m soaking it all up and being grateful for every experience 🤍 anyone else feel that way?!

node.text:
Been in bed all day 😆 but channeling this energy this week 💁🏼‍♀️💅🏻

Not feeling too great and I’m exhausted but I always try to channel my best, most put together self whenever I’m feeling this way and I swear it helps !! also have some new favorite quotes that help me so wanted to share in case they help any of you too 🤍 
- your growth frightens people who have no plan on changing 
- slow progress is still progress (love this one)
- you’re capable of creating the life you can’t stop thinking about 
- simplify your life. cut out distractions or anything that doesn’t make you feel good and prioritize what makes you happy. 

Not sure if you guys like hearing the quotes that help push and motivate me but lmk if this was helpful and I can share more ☺️

node.text:
2 years ago today I met my soulmate @therealtarekelmoussa ❤️

Today was already a special day celebrating our freedom but it’s extra special because it’s the day I met the love of my life. I was down in Newport celebrating the 4th with some of my friends and we ended up jumping on Tarek’s boat and the rest is history ☺️ I know a lot of you know that story but I still get chills every time I think about it and it just goes to show that you never know what life has in store for you. 🤍 So on that note I hope everyone has a beautiful, safe, and happy 4th and cheers to my future husband on creating our dream life together… I love our love. ❤️🥰
